nsport of DCVs developed in our paper\ncan be used to model the transport of other organelles in axons.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Mar 2019 03:44:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 2 May 2019 17:57:58 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 7 Sep 2019 14:33:09 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sat, 1 Feb 2020 18:36:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-04"}
