 The system has been used to\nmeasure currents ranging from 500 pA to 5 $\\mu$A and capacitances between 5 pF\nand 100 pF. A precision of better than 0.2 pF on capacitance measurements in\nthat range can be achieved. Examples of calibration and measurement results for\nleakage current and capacitance are presented.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Mar 2019 12:10:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 26 Feb 2021 10:29:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-01"}
